{"tid":542694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲大陸人點解可以有多張ATM卡？","createTime":"2018-01-27T17:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T17:43:19.000Z","uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85483f025165b4b05847ff24973cb722c5c338d2","tid":542694,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"今日喺尖沙咀諗住㩒錢，點知前面個大陸女人攪咗好耐，我就睇下佢做吔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來佢不停喺褲袋攞唔同嘅銀行卡出嚟，但只喺check balance，但又唔㩒錢。我見到啲 balance 都喺得果幾千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋佢起碼有7-8張卡<br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住問佢，小姐你重有幾多張要㩒，佢就急急腳走了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知佢做吔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ecd3320728f08d190060fbc581e14b020b6700","tid":542694,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"【內地人集體在港ATM大額提款】<br />\n【金管局:正密切監察】<br />\n<br />\n本港部分櫃員機近日有內地人集體大額提款。<br />\n<br />\n金管局指，早前澳門針對提取港幣的內地持卡人，在櫃員機引進人臉識別技術，或導致提取現金活動轉移至本港。<br />\n<br />\n國家外匯管理局今年起，將內地持卡人境外提取現金的最高金額，改為每人每年 10 萬元人民幣，亦可能影響在本港櫃員機提取現金的金額。<br />\n<br />\n金管局表示正密切監察，但就指代他人從櫃員機提取現金，不屬違法，不應假設所有提款活動都涉及犯罪或洗錢行為。<br />\n<br />\n若銀行發現有可疑，須向警方報告。<br />\n<br />\n金管局亦向澳門了解，在櫃員機使用人臉識別技術的經驗，正評估相關成效及可靠性，現階段無計劃引入相關技術。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#櫃員機　#內地人　#集體大額提款 #金管局　#密切監察　#提款情況<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=791482177710519&amp;id=186040714921338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D791482177710519%26id%3D186040714921338&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c2a310f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=791482177710519&amp;id=186040714921338</a>"},{"pid":"46eddaba6547b48bb074b03281e27375a8ca2b48","tid":542694,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"一係走資 一係洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5413ae68c32a36993caec2f89df48d2d71796c3e","tid":542694,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46eddaba6547b48bb074b03281e27375a8ca2b48","tid":542694,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"一係走資 一係洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"但佢又唔㩒錢出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}